					</listitem>
					 <listitem>
						<para>
							Are net controls and operators being rotated
						</para>
					</listitem>
					 <listitem>
						<para>
							Is there evidence of a plan to rotate operators
						</para>
					</listitem>
					 <listitem>
						<para>
